content: Hi,  yesterday I trained for texting and not sure where to go from here. I did not get a link. Unsure how to start. thanks!
Hi, Marian. <@477560366432256000> Could you or another text mod help?
Can you add your display name.
You'll want to edit your server profile to your first & last name. If you right click your name in the members section <a:arrow4:1269736547213901865> there should be "Edit Server Profile"

"We ask that everyone has a first and last name listed as their Display Name in Discord. This is important so we can quickly assign you texts if needed, or take a look at a conversation if you have a texting question. You don't need to use your real last name if you prefer not to - it just has to be the same last name in Discord and in Scale to Win!"
I added my last name. Can you check to see if I did this correctly? Sorry, but I have to use my real last name and it has to be the same in discord. I'm  just not following what needs to be done.
That's perfect! Jack should be able to assist when he has a moment.
You should be added in 24-72 hours from the point that you took the training.
